    <aside><title>Note</title> <p>The Pasco Capstone interface is also used in <xref ref="c-acceleration" text="type-hybrid" />, <xref ref="c-friction" text="type-hybrid" />, and <xref first="c-energy-1" last="c-energy-2" text="global">Labs</xref>.  You should start becoming familiar with the hardware and software.</p></aside>
    <p>
    <ul>
    <li><p> Take data with Capstone and the motion sensor as the cart travels with constant acceleration down the track.
        Determine the acceleration of the cart from a linear regression using the velocity vs time data (a linear fit line in Capstone).
