    <li><p> Collect 7 data runs, where about 2-5 grams<fn xml:id="fn-penny-date">Pennies are a reasonable mass to be moving.  If you are provided with pennies as the mass being transferred, then (after finding the individual mass of each) you might consider using the date of minting to distinguish which penny was transferred in order to determine the specific mass each time.</fn>
     is transferred each time from the cart to the hanging mass.
        Determine the acceleration of the cart (and the uncertainty for the acceleration) for each of these 7 runs.</p></li>
